  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/420eb2f1ed962979c8f71b062384bf85.avif?t=1657894249\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><strong>COMPLETE YOUR REVENGE NO MATTER HOW MANY TIMES YOU FAIL</strong><br>Failing can become quite common on your journey, unless you really are the boogeyman.<br>                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/36779016596c1885c39ddd47d778cd97.poster.avif?t=1657894249\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/36779016596c1885c39ddd47d778cd97.webm?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/36779016596c1885c39ddd47d778cd97.mp4?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>ARE YOU FAST ENOUGH? </strong><br>John Brick is a game with a very simple and challenging mechanics, just be quick between shooting and protecting yourself<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/f45ca674ff2e53474850b9e453461346.poster.avif?t=1657894249\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/f45ca674ff2e53474850b9e453461346.webm?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/f45ca674ff2e53474850b9e453461346.mp4?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>TOO HARD?</strong><br>By killing enemies, you get enough money to buy upgrades that will make it a lot easier.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/77fc2337ad30f72104b69692ba752731.poster.avif?t=1657894249\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/77fc2337ad30f72104b69692ba752731.webm?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/77fc2337ad30f72104b69692ba752731.mp4?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>... OR TOO EASY?</strong><br>The difficulty of the levels rises with the passage of the stages, with new mechanics. There will always be a new difficulty!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/9c3904b277deb28c42bf5ccf981c5955.poster.avif?t=1657894249\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/9c3904b277deb28c42bf5ccf981c5955.webm?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/9c3904b277deb28c42bf5ccf981c5955.mp4?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR BRICK </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/2efe28724fc4054bc4fb5e7667c80f11.poster.avif?t=1657894249\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/2efe28724fc4054bc4fb5e7667c80f11.webm?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2065090/extras/2efe28724fc4054bc4fb5e7667c80f11.mp4?t=1657894249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
